description.en: Autonio Foundation is a decentralized autonomous organization built around developing accessible, easy to use and affordable trading tools. These tools make it easier for crypto traders to conduct trading analysis, deploy trading algorithms, exchange crypto currencies, sell their strategies and pool funds for trading purposes, all with profitability, security and ease.
